queries.sql: SELECT s.scu_id as id, s.scu_nombre as nombre, s.scu_idcue as cuenta, s.scu_estado as estado, c.cue_nombre as cueNombre FROM scu_sub_cuenta as s INNER JOIN cue_cuenta as c ON s.scu_idcue = c.cue_id ;

SELECT s.sre_id as id, s.sre_nombre as nombre, s.sre_telefono1 as telefono1, s.sre_telefono2 as telefono2, s.sre_telefono3 as telefono3, s.sre_correo as correo, s.sre_direccion as direccion, s.sre_idreg as idRegion, s.sre_estado as estado, p.per_nombre as nombre_del_responsable, r.reg_nombre as idRegion FROM sre_sub_region s INNER JOIN per_personal p ON s.sre_idper_responsable = p.per_id INNER JOIN reg_region r ON s.sre_idreg = r.reg_id
